sequenceDiagram
    participant Inspector as Financial Authority/Inspector
    participant TSE as TSE
    participant Storage as Storage Medium
    participant ERS as Recording System

    Note over Inspector: Tax Audit or<br/>Field Inspection

    Inspector->>TSE: exportLogMessages()<br/>(no authentication required)
    activate TSE
    
    TSE->>TSE: Check: Data available?
    
    TSE->>Storage: Read all Log Messages
    activate Storage
    Storage-->>TSE: Transaction-Logs<br/>System-Logs<br/>Audit-Logs
    deactivate Storage
    
    TSE->>TSE: Get Certificate Chain
    TSE->>TSE: Create TSE Information (info.csv)
    
    TSE->>TSE: Pack TAR Archive:<br/>- Log Messages (*.log)<br/>- Certificates<br/>- info.csv
    
    TSE->>TSE: Generate Filename according to Schema:<br/>[SERIALNUMBER]_[TIMESTAMP].tar
    
    TSE-->>Inspector: TAR Archive + Filename
    deactivate TSE
    
    Note over Inspector: Save TAR Archive locally
    
    Inspector->>Inspector: Open TAR Archive
    Inspector->>Inspector: Read info.csv
    Inspector->>Inspector: Extract Certificates
    Inspector->>Inspector: Extract Log Messages
    
    Note over Inspector: Further Processing:<br/>Verification, Audit
